:0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"9號晚有無手足被捕？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:51:45.000Z","msg":"警方今日(11日)下午舉行記者會，指共 19 人被捕，其中有 7 名男子在立法會示威區被拘捕，涉參與非法集會；另外警方隨後再拘捕 10 男 2 女，涉嫌堵路。被捕者年齡介乎 19 至 34 歲，大多數為廿歲左右的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警察將示威人士從立法會範圍驅散後，今晨再於灣仔告士打道一帶截留共 358 人，他們一度被警方搜身及記錄身分，當中包括 263 男及 95 女， 其中 16 至 25 歲佔 291 人，佔被截留者 81%，當中 18 歲以下的有 24 人。警方相信他們曾參與當晚較早前在立法會舉行的非法集會，強調會繼續進行調查，「有決心」將所有滋事人士繩之於法，絕不姑息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/6-10-%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-19-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91-9-%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%AD-2-%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-10-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-19-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591-9-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD-2-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8JuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=f67694d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-10-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-19-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591-9-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD-2-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&h=e174c7f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/6-10-%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-19-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91-9-%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E7%95%B6%E4%B8%AD-2-%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"e96a5b65de20da8e04d557eb6e840454cf5b8bb5","tid":1241093,"uid":180462,"lik